Iron Tyrant									KEY:Antipaladin Archetype ~ Iron Tyrant					CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.AntipaladinArchetype										PRECLASS:1,Antipaladin=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Antipaladin Archetype ~ Iron Tyrant],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Antipaladin_Archetype_TouchOfCorruption=True,Antipaladin_Archetype_Cruelty=True,Antipaladin_Archetype_ChannelNegativeEnergy=True,Antipaladin_Archetype_FiendishBoon=True]																																																								DESC:Covered from head to toe in blackened armor decorated with grotesque shapes and bristling with spikes, iron tyrants make an unmistakable impression on the battlefield. These antipaladins' armor is an outward symbol of their inner power, and they are rarely seen without it. Iron tyrants seek the strength to rule over domains as unfettered despots, and depend on their armor as protection against those they have not yet cowed.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Iron Tyrant ~ Iron Fist|PRECLASS:1,Antipaladin=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Iron Tyrant ~ Bonus Feats|PRECLASS:1,Antipaladin=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Iron Tyrant ~ Unstoppable|PRECLASS:1,Antipaladin=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Iron Tyrant ~ Fiendish Bond|PRECLASS:1,Antipaladin=5																																																																																																																																																																																																																												COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.4																								FACT:Antipaladin_Archetype_TouchOfCorruption|true	FACT:Antipaladin_Archetype_Cruelty|true	FACT:Antipaladin_Archetype_ChannelNegativeEnergy|true	FACT:Antipaladin_Archetype_FiendishBoon|true