Deflective Shield								KEY:Knight of Arnisant ~ Deflective Shield				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Features.KnightofArnisantClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A knight of Arnisant specializes in using his shield to deflect attacks. He adds a bonus equal to his shield bonus to AC to his touch AC and his CMD, up to a maximum of half his cavalier level. He does not include any enhancement bonus he has from a magic shield in this calculation.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Heraldic Banner								KEY:Knight of Arnisant ~ Heraldic Banner					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Features.KnightofArnisantClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A knight of Arnisant uses his shield as a banner, though its benefits apply only to allies within 30 feet. This ability alters banner.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Soul Shield									KEY:Knight of Arnisant ~ Soul Shield					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Features.KnightofArnisantClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:When carrying a shield, a knight of Arnisant adds a bonus equal to his shield bonus to AC on all saving throws against curse spells and effects, up to a maximum of half his cavalier level. He does not include any enhancement bonus from a magic shield in this calculation.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Defensive Challenge							KEY:Knight of Arnisant ~ Defensive Challenge				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Features.KnightofArnisantClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Whenever a knight of Arnisant declares a challenge, his target must pay particular attention to him. As long as the target is within the threatened area of the cavalier, it takes a -2 penalty on attack rolls against anyone other than the knight of Arnisant.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.6
Heart Shield								KEY:Knight of Arnisant ~ Heart Shield					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Cavalier Class Features.KnightofArnisantClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:When carrying a shield, a knight of Arnisant adds a bonus equal to his shield bonus to AC on saving throws against death spells and magical death effects, up to a maximum of half his cavalier level. He does not include any enhancement bonus from a magic shield in this calculation.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.6

