Yojimbo									KEY:Samurai Archetype ~ Yojimbo						CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.SamuraiArchetype										PRECLASS:1,Samurai=1		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Samurai Archetype ~ Yojimbo],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Samurai_Archetype_Mount=True,Samurai_Archetype_WeaponExpertise=True,Samurai_Archetype_MountedArcher=True]																																																																				DESC:Yojimbo are highly trained bodyguards favored by the nobles and warlords of distant Minkai. Yojimbo who follow the order of the warrior loyally guard a single master, while ronin serve whoever can pay for their protection.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Yojimbo ~ Resolute Defense|PRECLASS:1,Samurai=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Yojimbo ~ Armor Expertise|PRECLASS:1,Samurai=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Yojimbo ~ Intercept|PRECLASS:1,Samurai=4																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.7																								FACT:Samurai_Archetype_Mount|true	FACT:Samurai_Archetype_WeaponExpertise|true	FACT:Samurai_Archetype_MountedArcher|true	FACT:Samurai_CF_Mount|true	FACT:Samurai_CF_WeaponExpertise|true	FACT:Samurai_CF_MountedArcher|true

Resolute Defense								KEY:Yojimbo ~ Resolute Defense						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Samurai Class Features.YojimboClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																													DESC:Whenever a yojimbo issues a challenge, he can select one ally as his ward for the duration of the challenge. Whenever the yojimbo is adjacent to his ward, he can use resolve, greater resolve, and true resolve on his ward rather than targeting himself.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.7
Armor Expertise								KEY:Yojimbo ~ Armor Expertise							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Samurai Class Features.YojimboClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																													DESC:[NOT IMPLEMENTED] A yojimbo selects one type of armor, such as chain shirt or scale mail. The yojimbo gains armor training, treating his samurai level as his fighter level, when wearing the selected armor.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.7
Intercept									KEY:Yojimbo ~ Intercept								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Samurai Class Features.YojimboClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																													DESC:A yojimbo learns to better disrupt the attacks of his enemies. He gains Bodyguard as a bonus feat, even if he does not meet the prerequisite. In addition, whenever the yojimbo uses the aid another action to increase an ally's Armor Class, the bonus to Armor Class from the aid another action increases by 1.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Bodyguard																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.7

